  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A retrospective study to compare clinical results of patients that were treated by Bipolar
      H.A. vs. closed reduction and internal fixation with Trochanteric Antegrade Nail for
      displaced femoral subcapital fracture.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
